{"tid":246312,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Zaza一小步助湧屌打馬刺","createTime":"2017-05-17T02:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T17:38:18.000Z","uid":83557,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fdf345bda1b7f89b3abc7ef1efa321543aa6cef","tid":246312,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:12:12.000Z","msg":"Zaza好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6630b3411aa099ca3a8ecdf4a61fe5e6c887dec","tid":246312,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmcgee仲勁過佢"},{"pid":"9771382c105f2e02d8780a554feb85bd26f76ffb","tid":246312,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:19:14.000Z","msg":"仲有harden同david lee一小步"},{"pid":"fe33e6367de8b15913ac03db7733c4766f90da56","tid":246312,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"Zaza嘅一小步，勇士嘅一大步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e44b205dbb7834e705bc8ed8fd86bbdf869dffe","tid":246312,"uid":2932,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:21:32.000Z","msg":"怎樣才算贏馬刺?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在馬刺顛峰期定勝負<br />\n2.要在馬刺內部沒有矛盾的時候<br />\n3.要在Kawhi Leonard狀態最好的時候<br />\n4.你不能以內線不停強攻<br />\n5.你不能玩三分雨<br />\n6.你不能防守反擊，你要全隊都攻出來，像勇士太陽<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給Kawhi Leonard足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能double team Kawhi Leonard<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向馬刺，最好一開場就給主隊主將一個T-foul<br />\n10.你不能有barnes，artest式的硬漢，要讓Kawhi Leonard的球順利過中場<br />\n11.Kawhi Leonard帶球，你不能幾個人去攔截，要讓Kawhi Leonard達陣<br />\n12.你不能碰到Kawhi Leonard，否則立即犯規<br />\n13.你進的球前要把馬刺每個隊員都過一遍，最好再由底線繞出來，然後再把球射進，這樣才是真水平，否則馬刺認為是靠運氣<br />\n14.你球員不能嘗試由中場射buzzer beater<br />\n15.你要允許教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n16.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，馬刺迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。馬刺迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。"},{"pid":"1dd461417bdc8380669a0882c725963540526c92","tid":246312,"uid":1437,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:23:47.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - 真人串過碼頭咕哩"},{"pid":"0247fb217b1500b56e85cc8be159981b756e8011","tid":246312,"uid":83557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nmcgee仲勁過佢</blockquote><br />\n呢個真 我都屌左成季Zaza廢<br />\n又進攻又防守冇籃板<br />\n但係嗰一腳真係好正常 冇得屌"},{"pid":"b52d549cff69cdcf2d80537397363ef630be779b","tid":246312,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>怎樣才算贏馬刺?<br />\n<br />\n1.要在馬刺顛峰期定勝負<br />\n2.要在馬刺內部沒有矛盾的時候<br />\n3.要在Kawhi Leonard狀態最好的時候<br />\n4.你不能以內線不停強攻<br />\n5.你不能玩三分雨<br />\n6.你不能防守反擊，你要全隊都攻出來，像勇士太陽<br />\n7.你不能壓迫式防守，要給Kawhi Leonard足夠的空間發揮<br />\n8.你不能double team Kawhi Leonard<br />\n9.在你的主場，你不能有主場哨，裁判要偏向馬刺，最好一開場就給主隊主將一個T-foul<br />\n10.你不能有barnes，artest式的硬漢，要讓Kawhi Leonard的球順利過中場<br />\n11.Kawhi Leonard帶球，你不能幾個人去攔截，要讓Kawhi Leonard達陣<br />\n12.你不能碰到Kawhi Leonard，否則立即犯規<br />\n13.你進的球前要把馬刺每個隊員都過一遍，最好再由底線繞出來，然後再把球射進，這樣才是真水平，否則馬刺認為是靠運氣<br />\n14.你球員不能嘗試由中場射buzzer beater<br />\n15.你要允許教練中場休息進裁判室交流<br />\n16.務必遵守以上守則，否則即使你不小心贏球了，馬刺迷也會說你是勝之不武，說你是靠運氣，說你無恥。馬刺迷總是可以找到一條理由來說明你不應該贏球。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />